label: Ny Carlsberg Brewhouse
description: The Ny Carlsberg Brewhouse was built by Carl Jacobsen as the new brewhouse of his Ny Carlsberg Brewery which he had founded after a conflict with his father, Carlsberg-founder J. C. Jacobsen.

http://data.duraark.eu/vocab/buildm/loca.@value: In the Carlsberg district of Copenhagen, Denmark, on the border between Vesterbro and Valby.
